notes.description: A Congressman works with his equally conniving wife to exact revenge on the people who betrayed him.
Level-headed son Michael Bluth takes over family affairs after his father is imprisoned. But the rest of his spoiled, dysfunctional family are making his job unbearable.
family of adult siblings find that their secrets and scars are revealed when their black sheep of a brother returns home.
woman is rescued from a doomsday cult and starts life over again in New York City.
